<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-06-11 21:03 </DATE_TIME>
<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Jewish group denies alleged Kremlin plot to oust Russia's top rabbi </HEADLINE>
By NICK WADHAMS
<TEXT>
